1. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) - The paper introduces a computational-level model of theory of mind (ToM) based on dynamic epistemic logic (DEL), which is a subfield of AI. 
2. cs.LO (Logic in Computer Science) - The paper uses dynamic epistemic logic (DEL) as the basis for the ToM model, which is a subfield of logic in computer science. 
3. cs.LG (Machine Learning) - The paper discusses the computational complexity of the ToM model, which is a common topic in machine learning. 
4. cs.MA (Multiagent Systems) - The paper considers the number of agents as a parameter in the complexity analysis, which is a key aspect of multiagent systems. 
5. cs.CC (Computational Complexity) - The paper provides a parameterized complexity analysis of the ToM model, which is a subfield of computational complexity.
